<ab facs="#facs_539_r1l21">er ſey ein <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_539_line_1592203833921_2254">bey eẅch </ab></add> ʒu Holuelt / wıe ein rede vnd ein <expan>leẅmu<ex>n</ex>t</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r1l22">Jm <expan>entſtande<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey / daʒ er <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>heımlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> knecht vnd kuntſchafter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r1l23">lange ʒeıt <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd noch ſein ſülle Tun wır <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r1l24">ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır niht <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> noch von <expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan> dem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> </ab>
