<ab facs="#facs_539_r1l27">wellet eẅch <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan cert="unknown">H</expan>  pıgnot darinn befolhen <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_line_1592203856660_2274"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_539_r1l30"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Om<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
